she started walking in the direction she thought Scorponok had taken 
to go after the mouse.  She tried her scanner, but it had been 
damaged in the fight. "Well, who ever it was, sure got one lucky shot 
on me.  Thank the Matrix it was my arm scanner and not my spark."
She walked on hoping to run into Scorponok.
